hadiths[9]{hadithnumber,text}:
2290,"(apne daure-khilaafat mein) unhein zakat wsool karne ke liye bhejaa. (jahaan wo zakat wsool kar rahe they wahan ke) aik shakhs ne apni biwi ki baandi se ham-bistarii kar li. Hamza ne uski aik shakhs se pahley zamaanat li, yahan tak ke wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us shakhs ko so kodon ki saza di thi. us aadmi ne jo jurm is par laga tha usko qabool kya tha lekin jahaalat ka uzr kya tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko ma'zoor rakha tha aur Jarir aur Ashas ne Abdullah-bin-Masood se murtadon ke barey mein kaha ke unse tauba karaaiye aur unki zamaanat talab kijiye (ke dobara murtad na hongey) chunanche unhon-ne tauba kar li aur zamaanat khud unhiin ke qabeele walon ne de di. Hammad ne kaha jiska hazir zaamin ho agar wo mar jaey to zaamin par kuchh taawaan na hoga. lekin hakam ne kaha ke zimme ka maal dena padega."
2291,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bani-Israeel ke aik shakhs ka zikr farmaya ke unhon-ne Bani-Israeel ke aik doosrey aadmi se aik hazaar Dinar qarz maangey . unhon-ne kaha ke pahley aisey gawah la jinki gawahi par mujhey eitibaar ho. qarz maangney wala bola ke gawah to bas Allah hi kafi hai phir unhon-ne kaha ke achchha koi zaamin laa. qarz maangney wala bola ke zaamin bhi Allah hi kafi hai. unhon-ne kaha ke tu ney sachchii baat kahi . chunanche us ne aik muqarrara muddat ke liye usko qarz de diya. ye sahib qarz lekar dariyaaii safar par rawaana huey aur phir apni zarurat poori karke kisi sawari (kishtii wghaira) ki talash ki taake us se dariya paar karke us muqarrara muddat tak qarz dene waley ke paas pahunch sakey jo isse tay paai thi. (aur iska qarz ada kar de) lekin koi sawari nahi milii. aakhir aik lakdi li aur is mein suraakh kya. phir aik hazaar Dinar aur aik (is mazmoon ka ( khat ke uski taraf se qarz dene waley ki taraf (ye Dinar bhejey ja rahe hain) aur uska munh band kar diya aur usey dariya par ley aaey, phir kaha, aey Allaah! to khub janta hai ke maine falan shakhs se aik hazaar Dinar qarz liye they. us ne mujh se zaamin maanga to maine keh diya tha ke mera zaamin Allah Taala kafi hai aur wo bhi tujh par razi hua. us ne mujh se gawah maanga to uska bhi jawab maine yahi diya ke Allah paak gawah kafi hai to wo mujh par razi ho gaya aur (tu janta hai ke) maine bahut koshish ki ke koi sawari miley jiske zariie'y mein uska qarz us tak (muddat muqarrara mein) pahuncha sakoon. lekin mujhey usmein kamiyabi nahi hui. isliye ab main usko terey hi hawale karta hun (ke to us tak pahuncha de) chunanche us ne wo lakdi jis mein raqam thi dariya mein baha di. ab wo dariya mein thi aur wo sahib ( qarzdaar) wapas ho chukey they. halaanki fikr ab bhi yahi thi ke kis tarah koi jahaz miley. jiske zariey wo apne Shahar mein ja sakein. dusri taraf wo sahib jinhoney qarz diya tha usi talash mein (bandargaah) aaey ke mumkin hai koi jahaz unka maal lekar aaya ho. lekin wahan unhein aik lakdi milii. wahi jismein maal tha. unhon-ne lakdi apne ghar mein iindhan ke liye ley li. lekin jab usey chira to usmein se Dinar nikley aur aik khat bhi niklaa. (kuchh dinon ke baad jab wo sahib apne Shahar aaey) to qarz-khaah ke ghar aaey aur (ye khayal karke ke shayad wo lakdi na mil saki ho dobaara) aik hazaar dena unki khidmat mein pesh kar diye aur kaha ke qism Allah ki! main to barabar isi koshish mein raha ke koi jahaz miley to tumharey paas tumhara maal lekar Pohnchon lekin us din se pahley jabke main yahan pahunchne ke liye sawar hua. mujhey apni koshishon mein kamiyabi nahi hui. phir unhon-ne puchha achchha ye to bataao ke koi cheez kabhi tum ne mere naam bheji thi? maqrooz ne jawab diya bata to raha hun aapko ke koi jahaz mujhey us jahaz se pahley nahi mila jis se main aaj pahuncha hun. is par qarz-khaah ne kaha ke phir Allah ne bhi aap ka wo Qarzaa ada kar diya. jisey aap ne lakdi mein bheja tha. chunanche wo sahib apna hazaar Dinar lekar khush khosh wapas lot gaey."
2292,"( Quran Majeed ki aayat ( ولكل جعلنا موالي‏ )) ke mutaalliq Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke) mawaalii (ke mana ( Wirse ke hain. aur ( والذين عقدت أيمانكم‏ ) (kaa qissa ye hai ke) muhajireen jab Madina aaey to muhajir Ansar ka tarka patey they aur Ansari ke naatedaaron ko kuchh na miltaa. us bhaaii-paney ki wjah se jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qaaim ki hui thi. phir jab aayat ( ولكل جعلنا موالي‏ ) huii to pehli aayat ( والذين عقدت أيمانكم‏ ) mansookh ho gaee. siwa imdaad, ta'awun aur khair-khuwaahii ke. albatta meeraas ka hukm (jo Ansar w muhajireen ke darmyan bhaaichaare ki wjah se tha) wo mansukh ho gaya aur wasiiyat jitni chahey ki ja sakti hai. (jaisi aur shakhson ke liye bhi ho sakti hai tehai tarke mein se wasiiyat ki ja sakti hai jo laagu ki jaayegi)"
2293,"jab Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey yahan aaey they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka bhai chaara Sad-bin-Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) se karaya tha."
2294,"maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya aapko ye baat malum hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya tha, Islam mein jahiliyat waley ( ghalat qism ke) ahad w paiman nahi hain. to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to khud Ansar aur Quraish ke darmyan mere ghar mein ahad w paiman karaya tha."
2295,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan Namaz padhney ke liye kisi ka janaaza aaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kya us maiyat par kisi ka qarz tha? logon ne kaha ke nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki namaaze-janaaza padha di. phir aik aur janaaza aaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, maiyat par kisi ka qarz tha? logon ne kaha ke haan, tha. ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ke phir apne sathi ki tum hi Namaz padh lo. abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah! unka qarz main ada kar doonga. tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki namaaze-janaaza padhai."
2296,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar Bahrain se (jiziya ka ( maal aaya to main tumhen is tarah donon lap bhar-bhar kar doonga lekin Bahrain se maal Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat tak nahi aaya phir jab iske baad wahan se maal aaya to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne elaan kara diya ke jis se bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka koi wada ho ya aap par kisi ka qarz ho wo hamarey yahan aa jaey. chunanche main hazir hua aur maine arz kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se ye wo baatein farmai thin. jisey sun kar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey aik lap bhar kar diya. maine usey shumaar kya to wo panch so ki raqam thi. phir farmaya ke iske 2 guna aur ley lo.
2297,"maine jab se hosh sanbhaalaa to apne waalidain ko isi deene-Islam ka perokar paya aur Abu-Saleh Sulaiman ne bayan kya ke mujh se Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne bayan kya. unse Yunus ne, aur unse Zohri ne bayan kya ke mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine jab hosh sanbhaalaa to apne waalidain ko deene-Islam ka perokar paya. koi din aisa nahi guzarta tha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey yahan subah w Sham donon waqt tashrif na latey hun. phir jab musalmanon ko bahut zyada takleef honey lagi to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi hijrate-Habsha ka irada kya. jab aap Barke-Ghimaad pahunchey to wahan aap ki mulaqat Qaara ke sardaar Maalik-ibne-Daghina se hui. us ne poochha, abu-Bakar! kahan ka irada hai? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska jawab ye diya ke meri qaum ne mujhey nikal diya hai. aur ab to yahi irada hai ke Allah ki zameen mein sair karun aur apne rab ki ibadat karta rahoon . is par Maalik-bin-Daghina ne kaha ke aap jaisa insan (apne watan se) nahi nikal sakta aur na usey nikala ja sakta hai. ke aap to mohtajon ke liye kamatey hain, sila rehmii kartey hain. majbooron ka bojh apne sar letey hain. mehman nawazi kartey hain. aur haadison mein haq baat ki madad kartey hain. aapko main aman deta hun. aap chaliye aur apne hi Shahar main apne rab ki ibadat kijiye . chunanche ibne-Daghina apne sath Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko lekar aaya aur Makka pahunch kar kuffaare-Quraish ke tamam ashraaf ke paas gaya aur unse kaha ke Abu-Bakar jaisa nek aadmi (apne watan se) nahi nikal sakta aur na usey nikala ja sakta hai. kya tum aisey shakhs ko bhi nikal doge jo mohtajon ke liye kamaata hai aur jo sila rehmii karta hai aur jo majbooron aur kamzoron ka bojh apne sar par leta hai. aur jo mehman nawazi karta hai aur jo haadison mein haq baat ki madad karta hai. chunanche Quraish ne ibn-Daghina ki aman ko maan liya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko aman de di. phir ibn-Daghina se kaha ke Abu-Bakar ko uski takeed kar dena ke apne rab ki ibadat apne ghar hi mein kar liya karein. wahan jis tarah chaahein Namaz padhein, aur Quran ki tilawat karein, lekin hamein un chizon ki wjah se koi takleef na pahunchaaein aur na iska izhar karein, kyonke hamein iska dar hai ke kahin hamarey bachchey aur hamari auratein fitne mein na pad jaaein. ibn-Daghina ne ye baatein jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko sunain to aap apne rab ki ibadat ghar ke andar hi karne lagey. na Namaz mein kisi qism ka izhar kartey aur na apne ghar ke siwa kisi dusri jagah tilawat kartey. phir Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kuchh dinon baad aisa kya ke aap ne apne ghar ke samney Namaz ke liye aik jagah bana li. ab aap zahir ho kar wahan Namaz padhney lagey aur usi par tilaawate-qur'aan karne lagey. to phir kya tha mushrekeen ke bachchon aur unki aurton ka majma' lagney laga. sab hairat aur tajjub ki nigahon se unhein dekhtey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) badey hi roney waley they. jab Quran padhney lagtey to aansuon par qaabu na rahtaa. is sura haal se badey-badey mushrekeene-Quraish ghabraaey aur sab ne ibn-Daghina ko bula bhejaa. ibn-Daghina unke paas aaya to un sab ne kaha ke ham ne to Abu-Bakar ko isliye aman di thi ke wo apne rab ki ibadat ghar ke andar hi karengey, lekin wo to zyadti par utar aaey aur ghar ke samney Namaz padhney ki aik jagah bana li hai. Namaz bhi sab ke samney hi padhney lagey hain aur tilawat bhi sab ke samney karne lagey hain. dar hamein apni aulad aur aurton ka hai ke kahin wo fitne mein na pad jaaein. isliye ab tum unke paas jao. agar wo is par taiyaar ho jayen ke apne rab ki ibadat sirf apne ghar ke andar hi karein, phir to koi baat nahi, lekin agar unhein us se inkar ho to tum unse kaho ke wo tumhari aman tumhen wapas kar dein. kyonke hamein ye pasand nahi ke tumhari aman ko ham tod dein. lekin is tarah unhein izhar aur elaan bhi karne nahi dengey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke iske ba'd ibn-Daghina abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha ke aapko malum hai wo shart jis par mera aap se ahad hua tha. ab ya to aap us shart ki hudood mein rahen ya meri aman mujhey wapas kar dein. kyonke ye mein pasand nahi karta ke Arab ke kanon tak ye baat pahunchey ke maine aik shakhs ko aman di thi lekin wo aman tod di gaee Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke main tumhari aman tumhen wapas karta hun main to bas apne Allah ki aman se khush hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un dinon Makka hi mein maujood they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey tumhari hijrat ka maqam dikhlaaya gaya hai. maine aik khaarii namkeen zameen dekhi hai. jahan khajoor ke baghaat hain aur wo pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan mein hai. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska izhar farma diya to jin musalmanon ne hijrat karni chahi wo pahley hi Madina hijrat karke chaley gaey. balke kuchh wo sahaba bhi jo Habsha hijrat karke chaley gaey they wo bhi Madina aagey Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) bhi hijrat ki taiyaariyaan karne lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya, jaldi na karo, ummeed hai ke mujhey bhi jald hi ijazat mil jaeygi Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon ! kya aapko uski ummeed hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, zaroor! chunanche Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intizar karne lagey, taake Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hijrat karein. unke paas 2 oont they, unhein char mahiney tak wo babool ke pattey khilaatey rahe."
2298,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jab kisi aisi maiyat ko laya jata jis par kisi ka qarz hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke kya usne apne qarz ke ada karne ke liye bhi kuchh chhoda hai? phir agar koi aapko bata deta ke yahan itna maal hai jis se qarz ada ho sakta hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski Namaz padhatey warna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) musalmanon hi se farma detey ke apne sathi ki Namaz padh lo. phir jab Allah Taala ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par fateh ke darwazey khol diye to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main musalmanon ka khud unki zaat se bhi zyada mustahiq hun. isliye ab jo bhi musalman wafat pa jaey aur wo maqrooz raha ho to uska qarz ada karna mere zimmey hai aur jo musalman maal chhod jaey wo iske waarison ka haq hai.
